                                "stop": 10.547,
                                "byte_start": 81920,
                                "byte_stop": 124134,
                                "text": "The opinion of the Court in No. 95-6556, Old Chief against the United States will be announced by Justice Souter."
                            }
                        ]
                    },
                    {
                        "start": 10.547,
                        "stop": 104.15,
